OL,3,CFuneral Costs: The Price of Dying
OL,5,FNext week is Dying Matters Awareness
OL,6,FWeek, and Adam Shaw has been
OL,7,Finvestigating the best ways to plan an
OL,8,Faffordable funeral and how we can
OL,9,Favoid pitfalls and scams.
OL,11,FPlanning a funeral can be one of the
OL,12,Fmost difficult times of our lives, and
OL,13,Fa recent news story in Hull has put
OL,14,Fthe funeral industry in the spotlight.
OL,15,FTwo people from Legacy Independent
OL,16,FFuneral Directors have been arrested
OL,17,Fon suspicion of prevention of lawful
OL,18,Fand decent burial, and it has re-
OL,19,Fignited calls for the funeral industry
OL,20,Fto be properly regulated.
