OL,3,CFuneral Costs: The Price of Dying
OL,5,FBut perhaps a more pressing issue is
OL,6,Fthe cost of funerals, with the most
OL,7,Frecent Sun Life Cost of Dying report
OL,8,Fshowing that for the first time in
OL,9,Fthree years, the cost of a basic
OL,10,Ffuneral in the UK has risen ` now
OL,11,Fstanding at #4,141 (up 4.7% on last
OL,12,Fyear). Over the last twenty years, the
OL,13,Fcost of a basic funeral has risen a
OL,14,Fwhopping 126%, far higher than the
OL,15,Frate of inflation, which was 72% over
OL,16,Fthe same period.
OL,18,FAnd increased funeral costs are having
OL,19,Fa significant impact on people,
OL,20,Fespecially in light of the cost of
OL,21,Fliving crisis.
