OL,3,CFuneral Costs: The Price of Dying
OL,5,FThe rise in the cost of funerals is
OL,6,Fattributed in part to general
OL,7,Finflation. With energy prices high,
OL,8,Fthe cost of cremations has risen, and
OL,9,Fmany local authority cemeteries have
OL,10,Fhad to raise the price of burial plots
OL,11,Fas they are running out of space.
