OL,3,CFuneral Costs: The Price of Dying
OL,5,FThe Competitions and Markets Authority
OL,6,Frecently reported that while the cost
OL,7,Fof funerals is up, it has not risen
OL,8,Fabove the rate of inflation, and the
OL,9,FCMA has said that this shows that its
OL,10,F2021 intervention, requiring all
OL,11,Ffuneral directors to clearly display
OL,12,Ftheir prices in branch and online, is
OL,13,Fcontinuing to have a beneficial impact
OL,14,Fon the costs paid by bereaved
OL,15,Frelatives when arranging a funeral.
OL,17,FTo keep funeral costs down, more
OL,18,Fpeople are now opting for a direct -
OL,19,For unattended - cremation, with these
OL,20,Fnow accounting for 1 in 5 funerals, up
OL,21,Ffrom just 3% of funerals in 2019.
