OL,3,CFuneral Costs: The Price of Dying
OL,5,FWe drop in on a session on the topic
OL,6,Fof sustainable funerals, and the
OL,7,Fsurprising cost benefits of having a
OL,8,Fgreen funeral. Attendees learn about
OL,9,Feco-friendly alternatives to
OL,10,Ftraditional coffins, including woollen
OL,11,Fshrouds and coffins made with
OL,12,Freclaimed wood from shipping pallets,
OL,13,Fand discover the concept of a natural
OL,14,Fburial where a body is not embalmed
OL,15,Fand avoids the use of non-
OL,16,Fbiodegradable material such as plastic.
