OL,3,CFuneral Costs: The Price of Dying
OL,5,FAnother way to save money when
OL,6,Fplanning a funeral is to shop around
OL,7,Fand seek quotes from multiple funeral
OL,8,Fproviders before making a decision.
OL,9,FOver 80% of people only look for a
OL,10,Fsingle quote before booking a funeral,
OL,11,Fand this could mean that they are not
OL,12,Fgetting the best price to meet their
OL,13,Fneeds. Rebecca Peach was inspired by
OL,14,Fher own experience of planning a
OL,15,Ffuneral for a family member, and the
OL,16,Fdifficulty she had finding price
OL,17,Finformation online, to establish the
OL,18,Ffuneral comparison website, The
OL,19,FFarewell Guide.
