OL,3,CFuneral Costs: The Price of Dying
OL,5,FWhile 70% of people make some
OL,6,Fprovision to pay for their funeral,
OL,7,Fonly half put aside enough to cover
OL,8,Fthe entire bill. That can leave
OL,9,Frelatives with a hefty bill to cover
OL,10,Fwhen someone passes away, so the
OL,11,Fadvice is: plan ahead, research the
OL,12,Fbest deals - and make sure you share
OL,13,Fyour wishes with your loved ones.
